    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And concerning the children of Israel and Judah, that dwelt in the cities of Judah,.... As for the supplement \"concerning\", I see no need of it; the sense is, that when the king's edict was known by the inhabitants of the cities in the country, as well as at Jerusalem: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "they also brought in the tithes of oxen, and sheep; according to the law in Leviticus 27:32. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "they also brought in the tithes of oxen, and sheep; according to the law in ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
