      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and the tithe of holy things, which were consecrated unto the Lord their God; which Jarchi understands of the second tithe the Levites were to give to the priests; but Kimchi of things consecrated to sacred uses, and no longer for their own, and which were even free from tithing: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and laid them by heaps: heaps upon heaps, such large quantities were brought in. ",
